            <li>We check refrigerant levels and test for leaks</li>
            <li>We inspect and clean evaporator and condenser coils</li>
            <li>We test electrical components including capacitors and contactors</li>
            <li>We verify thermostat operation and calibration</li>
            <li>We check airflow and ductwork for restrictions</li>
            <li>We provide upfront pricing before any repairs</li>
          </ol>

